<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="wrong-n">wrong <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɒŋ/    美 /rɔːŋ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>坏事；过失：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Her son can do no wrong</strong> in her eyes.
在她眼里，自己儿子不可能做错事。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the difference between right and wrong 
是非之分</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If you’re the person who is <strong>in the wrong</strong>, just admit it!
如果你是理亏的那个人，尽管承认吧！</p><footer>2015 福建</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>不公正的事；冤屈：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They have <strong>done me</strong> a great <strong>wrong</strong>. 
他们对我非常不公平。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>wrongly  /'rɒŋli/ adv   </p></div>